name: Gunnison Copper Corp
longDescription: Excelsior Mining Corp is a Canada-based company which is engaged in exploration and development of copper. The firm's primary project is Gunnison Project and it operates through segments acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of mineral properties in North America.
